guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-treasurys-sanctions-office-hacked-by-chinese-government-washington-post-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>新奥尔良卡车袭击事件增加了类似事件的数量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vehicle-attacks-pedestrians-increasingly-common-around-world-2025-01-01/</link><description>车辆袭击变得越来越普遍，尽管只有其中一些被宣布为恐怖主义行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 17:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vehicle-attacks-pedestrians-increasingly-common-around-world-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>普京命令俄罗斯政府和顶级银行与中国发展人工智能合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已命令俄罗斯政府和该国最大的银行俄罗斯联邦储蓄银行与中国在人工智能领域建立合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>2024年，中国迎来几十年来最热的一年，再次打破纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/2024-china-saw-warmest-year-decades-breaking-records-yet-again-2025-01-01/</link><description>中国气象数据显示，2024年是该国自六十多年前有可比记录以来最热的一年，这是连续第二年打破里程碑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/2024-china-saw-warmest-year-decades-breaking-records-yet-again-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴将以16亿美元将高鑫零售股份出售给DCP</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-alibaba-sell-sun-art-stake-dcp-16-billion-2025-01-01/</link><description>中国阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司周三表示，已同意以 122.98 亿港元（15.8 亿美元）的价格将其在连锁超市高鑫零售集团的多数股权出售给中国私募股权公司 DCP Capital。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 12:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-alibaba-sell-sun-art-stake-dcp-16-billion-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>澳门 2024 年赌场收入高于官方预期，但低于大流行前的水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/macau-2024-casino-revenues-top-official-estimate-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2025-01-01/</link><description>全球最大的博彩中心澳门的赌场收入在 2024 年猛增近四分之一，但仍低于大流行前的水平，突显这个前葡萄牙殖民地需要实现经济多元化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 10:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/macau-2024-casino-revenues-top-official-estimate-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩出席新年庆祝活动并收到中国习近平的贺卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-attends-new-years-celebrations-with-daughter-kcna-2025-01-01/</link><description>据官方媒体朝中社周三报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩和他的女儿珠爱参加了新年庆祝活动，包括烟花和冰舞表演。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 10:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-attends-new-years-celebrations-with-daughter-kcna-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>哈萨克斯坦队在联合杯半决赛中终结德国队和美国队的卫冕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/kazakhstan-end-germanys-title-defence-united-cup-2025-01-01/</link><description>周三，哈萨克斯坦队在联合杯上终结了德国队的卫冕，而首届冠军美国队也在混合团体网球锦标赛中击败中国队进入了四强。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 06:59:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/kazakhstan-end-germanys-title-defence-united-cup-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示中国12月新房价格涨幅略快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-december-new-home-prices-rise-touch-faster-survey-shows-2025-01-01/</link><description>周三的一项私人调查显示，12月份中国新房价格上涨速度略快，受危机打击的房地产行业在政府一系列支持性政策的推动下艰难寻找底部。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 02:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-december-new-home-prices-rise-touch-faster-survey-shows-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>行业低迷加深，中国2024票房收入暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/china-2024-box-office-revenue-plunges-industry-downturn-deepens-2025-01-01/</link><description>周三官方数据显示，中国2024年票房收入同比下降近四分之一，对尚未从疫情中完全恢复的国内电影业造成打击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 02:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/china-2024-box-office-revenue-plunges-industry-downturn-deepens-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统希望与中国交流，但认为缺乏善意</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-says-he-welcomes-exchanges-with-china-2025-01-01/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周三表示，他欢迎与中国进行平等、有尊严、健康和有序的交流，但他想知道北京是否有善意，因为他所说的北京对旅游业等简单的事情进行了封锁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 01:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-says-he-welcomes-exchanges-with-china-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥公布新关税，Shein、Temu 等热门电子零售商可能成为瞄准目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-unveils-new-tariffs-popular-e-tailers-like-shein-temu-may-be-crosshairs-2024-12-31/</link><description>墨西哥税务机关 SAT 周二发布了新关税，称新关税将加强对来自亚洲的商品的监管，这一措施可能会影响 Shein 和 Temu 等热门在线零售商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 19:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-unveils-new-tariffs-popular-e-tailers-like-shein-temu-may-be-crosshairs-2024-12-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>